result.title: View solutions in GYM contests by creating group(if you can't enable coach mode of course)
result.content: Don't know if this topic has already been discussed here or not, but this information might be helpful to many. It is possible to view solutions in GYM contests by anyone who can create a group. Just create a group if you don't have one already then add the contest to your group. Now as the manager of that contest, you can view any source code.
